th on Quran: Last two verses of al-Baqarah sufficient","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites the last two verses of Surat al-Baqarah in the night, it is enough for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5051, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 807 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35879,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/parable-baqarah-ali-imran\/","url_meta":{"origin":32703,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Parable of Surat al-Baqarah and Ali \u2018Imran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLearn Surat al-Baqarah, for adhering to it is blessed, leaving it is sorrow, and the sorcerers cannot defeat it. Learn al-Baqarah and Ali \u2018Imran, for they are both the brightly illuminated chapters coming on the Day of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35874,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/shaytan-surah-al-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32703,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Satan does not enter with Surat al-Baqarah recited","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRecite Surat al-Baqarah in your houses, for Satan does not enter a house in which Surat al-Baqarah is recited.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2162 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3908,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/31\/al-baqarah-ali-imran-barakah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32703,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Recite al-Baqarah and Ali Imran, two blessed chapters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRecite the Quran, for on the Day of Resurrection it will come as an intercessor for its reciters. Recite the two brightly illuminated chapters, Surat al-Baqarah and Ali 'Imran, for on the Day of Resurrection, they will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35870,"url":"https:\